# Java conventions

Import order: `java.*` / `jakarta.*` → `io.quarkus.*` → third-party → `dev.vepo.passport.*`.

- Formatting: [passport-format-imports.mdc](passport-format-imports.mdc).
- Strings: [passport-strings.mdc](passport-strings.mdc).
- Prefer `var` when type is obvious; records for DTOs.
- SLF4J logging; no secrets in logs.
- Entities in `model/` package; `Instant` timestamps on `User`.

Domain naming: [domain-model.mdc](domain-model.mdc).
